'''Sotir "Til" Shkurti''' (born 24 January 1962) is an [[Albania]]n retired footballer, who played his entire professional career as goalie for [[Besa Kavajë]] football club.

==International career==
He made his debut for [[Albania national football team|Albania]] in an October 1987 Euro Championship qualification match against [[Romania national football team|Romania]] and earned a total of 4 caps, scoring no goals.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://eu-football.info/_player.php?id=19157|title=Player Database}}</ref>

His final international was a September 1990 friendly match against [[Greece national football team|Greece]].

